<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mentor Application Approved – Graphora</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #0f0f0f;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669 0%, #047857 100%);
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 26px;
        }

        .header p {
            margin: 8px 0 0;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 36px 32px;
            color: #e0e0e0;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #fff;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .steps {
            background: #242424;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px 24px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .step {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 16px;
            padding: 12px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #2e2e2e;
        }

        .step:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .step-num {
            background: #059669;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 28px;
            height: 28px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 13px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .step-text {
            color: #ccc;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .step-text strong {
            color: #fff;
        }

        .btn {
            display: block;
            width: fit-content;
            margin: 24px auto;
            padding: 14px 36px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669, #047857);
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #111;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #555;
            border-top: 1px solid #222;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #6366f1;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🎉 You're Approved as a Mentor!</h1>
            <p>Welcome to the Graphora Mentor Community</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Congratulations, {{mentorName}}!</h2>
            <p>We're thrilled to welcome you as an official Graphora mentor. Your application has been reviewed and
                approved. You can now start accepting sessions and helping students ace their interviews.</p>

            <div class="steps">
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-num">1</div>
                    <div class="step-text"><strong>Complete your profile</strong> – Add your photo, bio, and expertise
                        areas to attract students.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-num">2</div>
                    <div class="step-text"><strong>Set your availability</strong> – Define your weekly schedule so
                        students can book sessions.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-num">3</div>
                    <div class="step-text"><strong>Set your pricing</strong> – Choose your rates for 30-min and 60-min
                        sessions.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-num">4</div>
                    <div class="step-text"><strong>Add payout details</strong> – Set up your bank account or UPI to
                        receive earnings.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-num">5</div>
                    <div class="step-text"><strong>Go live!</strong> – Enable "Accepting Bookings" and start receiving
                        session requests.</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="btn">Go to Mentor Dashboard</a>

            <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #666; text-align: center;">Questions? Our team is here to help you get
                started.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            <p>© 2025 Graphora. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>